---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  description="Agricam - Detailed information about our flagship solution."
  title="Agricam | SmartIView"
>
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-[120px] bg-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Agricam</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Detailed information about Agricam, our flagship solution for monitoring livestock health.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Detailed information about Agricam -->
      <div class="w-full mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <img src="/assets/solutions/Agricow.jpg" alt="Agricam" class="mb-4 w-full rounded-lg shadow-md" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Agricam</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-4">Agricam is a smart AI camera designed for monitoring livestock health. It is especially useful to livestock farmers for preventing and drastically reducing mortality rates.</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4">
            <li>Real-time monitoring of livestock behavior</li>
            <li>Early detection of illnesses</li>
            <li>Instant alerts to farmers</li>
            <li>Data analytics for better decision making</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Agricam leverages advanced AI technology to provide farmers with the tools they need to ensure the health and well-being of their livestock.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>